        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'> I paired up with another necro in SF last week, we had more balls than brains (I was 41 he was 42).  But we did manage to take down one mob fear kiting before running away with our proverbial tails between our legs.</P><P>There's a fairly safe spot if you zone in from OT, off to the right of the doorway.  It's kind of a raised ledge area.  We pulled a spermy up there, sent pets, got him all DOT'd up and between the 2 of us fearing were able to kill him in about 4 minutes.  </P><P>Then we tried a chromodrac.... and ran.</P><P><BR> </font></td>
      </tr>
      <TR>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'
 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>Glonoin</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'> From the OT zone (invis first) go left about 200 feet (down the slope, towards the zone corner.)  You will be between a shrine to the allmighty dragon (big bronze statue with a globe above his wings if I recall) and the wall - there is a fairly open flat area - just past that (as you are about at the far end of the dragon shrine platform) that has a pillar - park your pet there.</P><P>Pull from the area between there and the zone, pull with a real light spell (I suggest your level 1 disease spell - prevents em from regen'ing hp during a fight and is easy for your pet to taunt offa you) and dooming when they get close to the pillar, fear.  Helps if you have two necros, the non-puller darknesses on the way in and the puller fears.  The mob walks to the wall, turns right, goes behind your pillar and hangs another right and dies if you have two pets, splurt, dooming darkness and fear.</P><P>Pretty good XP through about 53 or 54</P><P></P><P><BR>...____________zone wall_________________________________________<BR>..|..............................................................<BR>..|.,,,,,,,,.......(commas designate mob path).............\.....<BR>..|,..._/Pillar.............................................|Lava<BR>..|,..O....---..............................................|river<BR>..|,,,,X..|\./|.Dragon Shrine Platform......................|....<BR>..|.......|.o.|.............................................|....<BR>..|........---..............................................\....<BR>..|..........................................................\...<BR>..|.......(Pull from here)....................................\..<BR>--|-------\....................................................\.<BR>OT|(raised)|.....................................................<BR>--|-------/......................................................<BR>..|........................................